The Jacobite K1 No 62005 'Lord of the Isles'
Whilst up in Scotland I took time out to photograph The Jacobite on one of the better days whilst on holiday.The locomotive on duty was K1 class No 62005 'Lord of the Isles' seen here just out of Glenfinnan.A beautiful part of the world this stretch of line runs through from Fort William-Mallaig.We spent a very enjoyable few hours on the beach at Morrar stunning scenery.
